   7:granularplayermod.h **** 
   8:granularplayermod.h ****  GranularPlayer class modified by K. Bloemer 2025 (renamed to GranularPlayerMod)
   9:granularplayermod.h ****   Changes:
  10:granularplayermod.h ****   - Applies the envelope to the individual grains instead of the whole audio sample
  11:granularplayermod.h ****   - Adds two additional envelopes (fast attack and slow attack, linear), and envelopes now use 512 
  12:granularplayermod.h ****   - Adds a stereo spread for each grain and left/right output getter functions
  13:granularplayermod.h ****   - Adds the ability to change the effective audio sample size 
  14:granularplayermod.h ****   - Adds "width" parameter that starts grains at a random point within the timeframe set by width p
  15:granularplayermod.h **** */ 
  16:granularplayermod.h **** 
  17:granularplayermod.h **** #pragma once
