  36:granularplayermod.h ****     Date: November, 2023
  37:granularplayermod.h **** 
  38:granularplayermod.h ****     Author: Vinícius Fernandes
  39:granularplayermod.h **** 
  40:granularplayermod.h ****     GranularPlayerMod is a lookup table player that provides independent time stretching and pitch 
  41:granularplayermod.h ****     via granulation.
  42:granularplayermod.h ****     Inspired by the grain.player object from else pure data's library.
  43:granularplayermod.h **** */
